              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The flux at the irradiation position was",
                "2.5 x 10**13 +/- 5% n/cm2/s.",
                "Alpha-shape factor for the epithermal neutron",
                "spectrum was determined by the dual-monitor",
                "method using the measured Cd ratios for",
                "55Mn(n,gamma)56Mn and 59Co(n,gamma)60Co reactions.",
                "Alpha=-0.10 for Ho-166 with uncertainty of 3.91%",
                "Westcott correction factor g=1.0004 for Mn-55,",
                " g=1.0003 for Co-59 and g=1.0020 for Ho-165."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "67-HO-165",
                "field_identifier": "NAT",
                "value": 1.0
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Natural holmium oxide (Ho2O3),",
                "manganese oxide (MnO2)and cobalt oxide (Co3O4) were",
                "mixed and dissolved. The sample was prepared by drying",
                "50 mu-l of the solution."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "        Two samples were irradiated with and without",
                "Cd cover(height/diameter =2, wall thickness = 1 mm)"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Irradiation time 10 min",
                "        Cooling time 2-4 h",
                "        Counting time 10-15 min.",
                "        Sample-detector distance 15-20 cm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Correction was applied for epithermal neutron",
                "spectrum shaping factor.",
                ".The neutron self-shielding factors were considered",
                "negligible due to the low weight of the sample material"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A p-type coaxial high-purity germanium",
                "detector with 80% efficiency relative to 3'' x 3''",
                "NaI(Tl) detector at 1332.501 keV."
              ]
            }
          ],
